  "text": "In this section we prove that counting the number of bases in a bicircular matroid is a #P-hard problem. Our proof is by means of a two step reduction from the problem of counting the number of perfect matchings in graphs, which is known to be #P-hard [CITATION_1] . Next we state the relevant counting problems in detail.",
